{"argument": "- **Lack of Strategic Advantage:** Acquiring Oxford Street does not contribute to a color set since no other green properties are owned, meaning there would be no rent bonus from potential monopolization. The investment would not immediately enhance rent income or provide strategic leverage against opponents.

